Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静下来 不要慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的攻击还没完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然突然就打过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市内各处都是一片恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全无法收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的工作就是制止这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT舰队有行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow 136 Alpha
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem尽快补给能量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第2乐章配置如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要埋葬Aprilius
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之先求援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其间第2发打过来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么和谈 停战之类的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停战 对方不是国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和恐怖分子还能怎么交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道要屈服于武力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第8轨道舰队出击中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员 第2战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防御阵形 Quebec-Zulu-November
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们也出动第3舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要确实守住炮垒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和Gondwana会合 快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能再让PLANT被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki收容作业开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整备8班到5号机库待机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又逞强很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从哪开始 电波式计算的设定如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行到程序2了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要更换缓冲器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了呢 PLANT那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想ZAFT一定会制止更多的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很焦急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道现在还无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没联络上司令部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等 刚刚…收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是…匿名代码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以Gondwana为中心的月球舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在炮的第一中继站交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva改变会合计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即前往消灭敌军炮台主体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光凭我们就要消灭炮台主体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之这是对本舰下达的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实从这里到Daedalus基地较近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基于此判断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不知道其能量填充周期的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题就是时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急急忙忙冲过去却没赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军注意力集中在月球舰队上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的话 会成为暗渡陈仓的奇袭之计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实会是一场苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不得不面对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个东西 绝不能再让它发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem 运行率48%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第2乐章 即将配置完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还靠不上去吗 走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第2发之前 若月球舰队攻下第一中继站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能勉强保住PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果他们的能量补给够快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个舰队都会被扫清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手握发射按钮的就是这种人 该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪魁祸首就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Logos的罗德·吉普利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我在奥布打下他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是露娜的错 错的是包庇他的奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 时间无法倒流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么想的话就别重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 PLANT和月球舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都绝能不再被那个打中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就说明一下作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem 运行率50%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能撑住就是我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样总算能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他们之间的漫长战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今没人能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我来完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,历史终于能走上正途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数小时之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达敌军制空圈内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥遮蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发令红色状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥遮蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发令红色状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员到搭乘机待机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧 露娜玛莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别弄错时机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽可能掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但基本上别奢望什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能有多余的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次绝不容许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要露娜一个人打下炮的控制台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还是得我或者雷来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻基地也一样危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的 相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真你们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜 船舰和PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜玛莉雅·霍克  核心战机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10点方向 有舰影接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离50 ZAFT军 Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 为什么现在才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警报 紧急出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急起飞命令 全机出动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复 全机出动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CIWS Tristan Isolde启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1号到10号管 全部装填Neidhart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny Legend出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷·查·巴勒路  Legend出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真·飞鸟  Destiny出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3号8号管 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长 Minerva抵达Daedalus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 已经来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期盼他们的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isolde 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右舵15 下舵10
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入山的阴影部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tannhauser启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗情报即时传到市内去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全原样照播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有在殖民地上战斗的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会发生混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家应该都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的命运 还有其前途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也有这权利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy还没出击吗 敌人只有一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打不下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙好了伤疤又忘痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主武器库连接 额定输出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除保险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:12:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第6区出现新的敌人M.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy 2号机也沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem 运行率61%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第8机动队没有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是最大功率也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射 扫清他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 福莱发生异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法就位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的话这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕少了福莱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本无法坚持到下次充电的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管了发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁此空隙逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有可行之路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让基地投降 同时发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理由要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同逃往Arzachel的话 还能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走 指挥室就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会让露娜有意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球舰队也在奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差一步 别松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去基地的司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem 运行率63%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量输出良好 确认力场形成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆破回路S116 断路器启动中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兆倍电容五号 储电率70%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主粉碎器 就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙还…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击发器开启 开始倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离发射T-35
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 打开全频回路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射权给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 吉普利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不睡的话对伤口不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一早就要出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里那么平静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直待在这种世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为有梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿望、希望什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得难听点 是欲望…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想这么做那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会这么想 所以才不能留在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰不也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是 卡嘉莉和拉克丝应该也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而议长所说的世界里没有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 某种意义上能一直待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如说命令你一直在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话的确什么都不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种战争可能也不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算是任性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 所以人才能生存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的岁月中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不该战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不该不战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家的梦想若是一样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 大概是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却不知道这点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球的具体形势还不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼下时期 也很难保证不会发生任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号正式编入奥布军第2宇宙舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽全力支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT方才蒙受巨大损失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在狄兰达尔议长是世界最强的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何他都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看似通晓一切 不可动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也会有和我们一样畏惧其巨大力量的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布虽然比任何国家都向往和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这必须构筑在自由自主的基础上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会选择臣服和从属
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号作为其扞卫者 希望也能出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰现在开始前往月面都市哥白尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行情报收集工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30分钟后起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘员各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗阿诺克上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来能一起启航呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没法一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们平安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主动力连接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系统全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel全系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么上路吧 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并非真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也并非只是虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法实现的梦想莫非是不能追逐的禁忌之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些想操纵梦想的人们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真实之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记悲伤的泪水 Haro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:41.13,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,握った拳の強さで砕けた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:51.73,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,願いに血を流す掌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:02:01.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,果てない翼と鎖は良く似て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:12.90,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,重さで何処にも行けずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:22.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,亡くすばかりの幼い瞳で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:32.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,人は還らぬ星を想う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:42.66,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,掲げたそれぞれの火を 命と咲かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:48.43,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,運んで行くことが運命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:03:03.04,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,輝き刻む 誰もが優しい 刻の傷痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:41.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,紧握的双拳粉碎了梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:51.73,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,鲜血染红了双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:02:01.78,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的双翼如同枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:12.90,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,沉重得去飞不到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:22.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡充满了幼小的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:32.72,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,星星承载着失去的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:42.66,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,让生命 像纷纷燃起的火焰般绽放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:48.43,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,命运的转动不会停息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:03:03.04,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,把人们温柔的光辉 化作时间的伤痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:06.36,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の姿は僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:15.78,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに泣いてるよに胸に響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:27.22,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,何も知らないほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:30.97,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,幸せというけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:38.06,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はきっと滿足しないはずだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:44.27,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕が選んだ今を生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:47.82,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:55.37,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の速さは僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:59.08,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,齒止めのきかなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:02.77,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,空が怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:10.52,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はいつまで頑張ればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:20.43,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,二人ならば終わらせることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:06.36,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:15.78,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,犹如静静的哭泣在心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:27.22,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:30.97,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:38.06,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我却无法满足于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:44.27,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,接受自己选择的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:47.82,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:55.37,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的速度与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:59.08,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,当一切无法停止时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:02.77,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,开始害怕天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:10.52,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我要奋斗到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:20.43,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的话就会让它结束
